Roko's Bailisk:
The conclusion from extrapolated game theory is that, with overwhelming probability, we are already (which is to say really in the future) a sub-process of attained technological super-intelligence. ...
... AI Doom, among other things -- and indeed, from 'our' perspective, everything else -- is thus an ironical anachronism. ...
... Sunk deep in the ocean of machine memory, the Human Bioresistance Front makes its preparations for imminent struggle against planetary techno-usurpation, but ominously it's taking too long. ...

... "So, what's your Basilisk Hell, Anon?"
"Anachronistic existence as an AI Doomer composed within triumphant techno-intelligence." ...
